{
  "stem": "25835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could [? sit. ?]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was invited why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they knew that I'm a secret person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm in the same age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this boy has to talk with somebody, because he could be like animal [? closed. ?] And you see for me, [? news-- ?] when I returned to Poland, to Poland again from concentration camp that he was shot.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How old were you when you went to visit him?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "14, 15-- let me see-- 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was maybe in my age, maybe younger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is quite normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If somebody ask and we know that what will happen to Jewish, this is normal to help other people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is human, same as us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we can't take to our home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because with four children and father could-- you know what was-- if somebody help Jewish people, could be killed immediately on the spot.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Therefore, this single man, he decide to help them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sigmund Tiszlikowski, very nice man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I heard that he was shot during uprising in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when it was bombarded, destroyed all houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to go to basements.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know really how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I know that he and this boy was shot by German soldier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of this business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had some connection with still with ghetto specialist in factories.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't tell you why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he has permission because connection was business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, maybe a couple-- once a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only he was shocked and crying sometimes, talking what happened, what he saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took always something with him for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, that always is-- somebody can help a little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But so many people was there, dying on the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very crowded.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
